item.title: CVE-2018-1280|2024-08-05T03:59:37.283Z -- pivotal -- greenplum%20command%20center
item.description: Pivotal Greenplum Command Center versions 2.x prior to 2.5.1 contains a blind SQL injection vulnerability. An unauthenticated user can perform a SQL injection in the command center which results in disclosure of database contents.
